title: Arbor Skateboards :: Product Profiles - Backlash 40
description:
The Backlash is a downhill design with a true kicktail. It features rocker that runs between the trucks, a snub nose design, and flush routed truck mounts to maintain turning angle while providing superior slide control. No limits - bomb, flip, slide - whatever.
Artist: Eric Waetzig

L: 40.00” W: 9.75” WB: 24.00”-26.625”
To learn more about the Backlash 40 visit: arborcollective.com/skateboards/products/backlash-40/
